text: Puerto Rico Highway 138 (PR-138) is a north–south bypass located west of downtown Coamo, Puerto Rico. This road extends from PR-155 to the junction of PR-14 with PR-153 and is known as Avenida Luis Muñoz Marín. ==Major intersections== ==See also== *List of highways numbered 138 ==References== ==External links== * 138 Category:Coamo, Puerto Rico
title: Puerto Rico Highway 138
